Subject: RE: [T2] unable to bleed front brakes - need help!!!

I strongly suspect that you've found at least one problem.
Sometimes they will pass minute amounts of fluid to make the brakes
work but not enough to refill the calipers after brake repair.  Replace
all four rubber lines to be safe.

George

